structure.unit: COUNTIES, CITIES, AND OTHER LOCAL UNITS

law.history: Repealed 2014 Ky. Acts ch. 92, sec. 314, effective January 1, 2015. -- Amended 1976 (1st Extra. Sess.) Ky. Acts ch. 14, sec. 123, effective January 2, 1978. -- Recodified 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 208, sec. 1, effective October 1, 1942, from Ky. Stat. secs. 3498, 3629a-4.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Arrested persons, where kept in cities of fourth or fifth class.
